Import from GIT one of the projects:

Java: https://github.com/IdanFridman/TransactionService
(maven + java8 required)

Nodejs: https://github.com/IdanFridman/UserSearchService
(bower + npm required)


Modify the project and create a Elasticsearch client app that receives User Login details and Index them

Each login contains:

1. Username (String)
2. Date (String)
3. location (String)

The index name is: your_app_name
The mapping type name is: login


* let ES generate the id automaticlly.

After finish create another api calls for full text search Terms via key of Username

When finished improve your task Index by using the bulk API as explained in the slides.



